A survey of 20 peoples' occupations:
1 Housewife who has never worked; 1 Private Home Help; 2 Salesmen; 1 Civil Servant (Post Office work); 1 Managing Director;wife is partner; 1 Sales Assistant (Shop); 1 Bank Manager; 2 Bank Workers; 1 Financial Director; 1 General Manager (Factory); 1 Draughtsman; 1 Electrical Engineer; 1 Playgroup Supervisor; 1 Teacher; 1 Unemployed young man, never worked; 1 Self-employed man (Plastics factory) 1 Secretary (wife of above);
Most of the above group were Office Workers going out of the village to work,travelling between 5 and 30 miles
